e":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:41:18.000Z","msg":"西利又向《衞報》表示：「如果其他國家早於英國向BNO港人打開懷抱，我國聲譽必蒙污。」<br />\n<br />\n612之後佢地應該一直搞梗嫁啦<br />\n香港問題方面老美之前吹過大雞叫盟友準備接收香港難民 雖然只係預警<br />\n但依加人大立國安法正式一國一制 真係好難唔做野 <br />\n最後美加台都接收bno人先 咁英國唔單止日落帝國 直情係未落帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8687e48b6b8e41f04604c567621869a4f2ac40","tid":2036452,"uid":24133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3b8d549ed171f01a747a9cc63eb2542c6bef024","tid":2036452,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24472cf12e52e2a822986b3846936649b44506af","tid":2036452,"uid":52429,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1fead5e04887a7f3eb8fb7342f1a0f7278dc583a","tid":2036452,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"我只可以同你哋講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望愈大, 失望愈大啊各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心你哋平常心啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"好有信心今次"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:08:31.000Z","msg":"其實依家西方係想避免我哋好似猶太人咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:42:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>樓主幫pin 唔該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n西方世界諗緊乜關你撚事咩五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扮夠關心我英未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>緣份捉緊迷失情感</strong></span> (舊名<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BBBBBBBBBBBBBB</strong></span>) #146030<br />\nP牌五毛 最近無咗個P<br />\n留意五毛新風向 分化香港同台灣追擊蔡英文<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&